BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-04-21T23:00:00&endDate=2026-04-22T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWINDRUSH LINE: Tuesday 21 and Wednesday 22 April\, after 2315 each evening\, no service between Surrey Quays and Clapham Junction / Battersea Park. Use local bus route 35 (for Denmark Hill\, Brixton\, Clapham High Street and Clapham Junction)\; bus route 37 (for Peckham Rye\, Brixton\, Clapham High Street and Clapham Junction)\; and bus route 381 (for Surrey Quays\, South Bermondsey\, Queens Road Peckham and Peckham Rye). For Wandsworth Road\, use Clapham High Street\, which is a short walk away. Last through trains: Surrey Quays to Clapham Junction 2307 (Departs Dalston Junction at 2249)\; Clapham Junction to Dalston Junction 2315
DTEND:20260422T002900Z
DTSTART:20260421T230000Z
SUMMARY:Windrush line: Part Closure
UID:8a02db85-4a57-4692-9365-b69127de2e6d@8a02.org
END:VEVENT
